        <div class="rounded-xl border border-ink-800 bg-ink-900/30 p-5"><h3 class="text-white font-bold text-sm">No Time Limit</h3><p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-400">Square Appointments free limits you. Acuity and Booksy are trial-only. InkFlow's free plan is yours to keep—no expiration, no credit card needed.</p></div>
