        <div class="rounded-xl border border-ink-800 bg-ink-900/30 p-5"><h3 class="text-white font-bold text-sm">Free Support</h3><p class="mt-2 text-sm text-gray-400">Support for free users within 24 hours. Migration help from any platform included.</p></div>
